Is there any reason why a module would not display on a blog post page template?

Here's my code and when I go to the page and inspect the source there's nothing being put on the page where this module code is. If I take everything out except the path and label it still doesn't work.

       {% module "module_172789598656025"
          path="/MyTheme/modules/related-posts",
          label="related-posts",
          select_blog=123123123123,
          style={
          "display" : {
            "button" : false
            }
          }
        %}

